Originally a co-founder of [[TheForce.net]], '''Paul Ens''' became the director of [[Lucas Online]], responsible for the official sites like [[StarWars.com]] and leading team members including [[Pablo Hidalgo]] and [[Bonnie Burton]].

In [[August]] [[2006]], he left Lucasfilm to become founder of a new comic book company called Red 5 Comics and join visual effects / animation company Satellite Studios.

He is also the author of the online ''[[Evasive Action]]'' webstrips, the mock website [[HoloNet News (original website)|HoloNetNews.com]], and co-writer of [[R2-D2: Beneath the Dome]].

He posts at the official site discussion boards under the name [[Ghent]].

